---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="招募資訊 - WZULTC" description="越南學伴招募 - 實習/志工機會">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-4">
        越南學伴持續招募中｜實習/志工機會一把抓！
      </h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Recruitment Info Section -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 pb-4 border-b-2 border-gray-100">
        ✨ 想成為越南學伴嗎？ ✨
      </h2>

      <!-- Poster -->
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <img
          src="/assets/poster.png"
          alt="招募海報"
          class="max-w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg mx-auto"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Recruitment Details -->
      <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p class="text-lg">
          會越南語＋華語的你，發光的時刻到了！陪伴新移工適應生活，同時拿下實習學分、志工服務時數及跨文化經驗，一次全包，機會別錯過！✨
        </p>

        <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4 space-y-2">
          <p class="font-semibold text-green-800">✅ 實習72小時（2學分）</p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-green-800">✅ 志工30/60小時（認列境外生獎學金志工時數）</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">👥 服務內容：</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>線上陪伴：分享生活與語言學習經驗，給自己家鄉來的朋友溫暖支持</li>
            <li>課程TA：協助華語/長照課程</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">💡 為什麼要加入？因為：</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>有意義｜傳遞善意</li>
            <li>超彈性｜時間自選</li>
            <li>能成長｜跨領域、拓視野</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">🌸 招募條件：</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>母語為越南語，會說華語</li>
            <li>樂於助人，願陪伴他人</li>
            <li>至少能完成30小時服務</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t-2 border-gray-100">
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-6">
            🎯 報名面試，立刻行動！👇
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="text-center">
              <a
                href="https://forms.gle/Rm1NccxT9kefsr438"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-block bg-teal-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors"
              >
                🔗 點此填寫報名表單
              </a>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <img
                  src="/assets/qrcode/qr_gform_enroll.png"
                  alt="報名表單 QR Code"
                  class="inline-block max-w-[150px] rounded-lg shadow"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <a
                href="https://line.me/ti/g/-gQ-mNKntG"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
              >
                💬 點此加入 LINE 學伴群組
              </a>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <img
                  src="/assets/qrcode/qr_line_vsgroup.png"
                  alt="Line 群組 QR Code"
                  class="inline-block max-w-[150px] rounded-lg shadow"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Back Link -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 font-medium transition-colors"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
        </svg>
        返回網站首頁
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
